  "body": "### Description\n\nSupport for vendor placeholder which can select the SQL scripts from {vendor} location.\r\n```\r\nquarkus.flyway.locations=classpath:db/migration/{vendor}\r\n```\r\n\r\nVendors can be automatically detected by flyway, and migration scripts will be executed accordingly.\r\n\r\nHere's how it works in spring-boot - [spring docs](https://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/2.1.1.RELEASE/reference/html/howto-database-initialization.html#howto-execute-flyway-database-migrations-on-startup).\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
